rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Mogugu if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Mogugu about the floating islands in Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Mogugu about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Mogugu about recent developments.

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0001
rows.name:
Mogugu hear there used to be lots of native peoples
around here besides just Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0002
rows.name:
Apparently that ring was part of big weapon that one
native people used to try and destroy other native
people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0003
rows.name:
Mira must have been scary place back then!
By the way, does friend agree that ring look
like gottagonut?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0004
rows.name:
Hmm? Friend has never heard of gottagonut?
Gottagonut is Nopon snack with hole in center that
gives jitters and makes Nopon run around in circles.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0009
rows.name:
Mogugu left family and everything else behind to
seek out ultimate in legendary cuisine with Mujiji.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0010
rows.name:
But once Ganglion show up, business crawled to
standstill and Mogugu started to go hungry...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0011
rows.name:
Soon Mogugu going to keel over and join the stars.
And then how will Mogugu find legendary cuisine?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0012
rows.name:
Come on, Mujiji! Hurry up and find legendary
fluffshroom... Save Mogugu from untimely demise...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0017
rows.name:
Once there was incredible native civilization that
managed to build huge kingdom in sky![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0018
rows.name:
But then civilization lost control of energy used to keep
kingdom aloft and SMASH! No more kingdom.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0019
rows.name:
Islands that friend sees are all that remain.
At least, that is what Mogugu has been told.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0020
rows.name:
Foolish old people. If they have enough energy to put
castles in sky, they should invest in delicious cuisine
instead![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG0021
rows.name:
Think of glorious gastronomical wonders that were lost
because ancient people wanted to waste technology on
blowing selves up instead! Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG1001
rows.name:
Mujiji brought back LOTS of yummy fluffshrooms
for Mogugu to eat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG1002
rows.name:
No wonder people call fluffshrooms legend.
Taste buds of Mogugu very satisfied![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG1003
rows.name:
However! ...Mogugu must continue epic quest for
delicacies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG1004
rows.name:
Mogugu is prepared to give up everything,
even life, in order to sample every last savory
substance on planet![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG2001
rows.name:
In order to travel with Mujiji and find legendary
cuisine, Mogugu had to abandon family.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG2002
rows.name:
True, Mogugu finally got to try legendary fluffshroom.
Mogugu had delicious culinary opportunity. Buuuut...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG2003
rows.name:
Well, look at Henahena. Henahena never leave home,
but now has lover who bring delicious food right to
Henahena every day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG2004
rows.name:
What if Mogugu made mistake? Maybe Mogugu could
have stayed with wifeypon and still found culinary
wonders. That all Mogugu ever really want... *sniff*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev058101_MSG2005
rows.name:
So be it! Mogugu going to wrap up some fluffshrooms
and bring them home to wifeypon right now![ST:wait ]
